        /**
         * Size of the linear-gradient per-draw uniform :
         *   startEnd (16) + viewport (16) + countPad (16) +
         *   positions (16 * 16) + colors (16 * 16) +
         *   clipShapeBounds (16) + clipShapeRadiiKind (16) +
         *   colorFilter* (6 * 16) = 688 bytes.
